		"description": "<p>Also at 3rd level, your connection to the divine grants you the power to cast spells. Sacred agents learn magic as a tool to fight their hidden battles, tapping into the same types of divine power wielded by clerics and heralds, but with an eye toward covert action.</p>\n<h2>Cantrips</h2>\n<p>At 3rd level, you know two cantrips of your choice from the divine, movement, or obscurement schools. These spells count as rogue spells for you.&nbsp;You learn an additional cantrip at 10th level.</p>\n<h2>Spell Slots</h2>\n<p>The Sacred Agent Spellcasting table shows how many spell slots you have to cast your spells of 1st-level and higher. To cast one of these spells, you must expend a slot of the spell&rsquo;s level or higher.&nbsp;You regain all expended spell slots when you finish a long rest.</p>\n<p><strong>Table: Sacred Agent Spellcasting</strong></p>\n<table style=\"width: 100%; height: 350px;\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 17.0819%;\"><col style=\"width: 23.8434%;\"><col style=\"width: 20.6406%;\"><col style=\"width: 8.54093%;\"><col style=\"width: 10.8541%;\"><col style=\"width: 9.60854%;\"><col style=\"width: 9.25267%;\"></colgroup>\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"text-align: center; height: 47.6px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 47.6px;\">Level</td>\n<td style=\"height: 47.6px;\">\n<p>Cantrips</p>\n<p>Known</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 47.6px;\">\n<p>Spells</p>\n<p>Known</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 47.6px;\">1st</td>\n<td style=\"height: 47.6px;\">2nd</td>\n<td style=\"height: 47.6px;\">3rd</td>\n<td style=\"height: 47.6px;\">4th</td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.8px; text-align: center;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">3rd</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">2</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">3</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">2</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">-</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">-</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">-</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.8px; text-align: center;\">\n<td st